      • onNavigationReady

        void onNavigationReady(boolean isRunning)
        Fired after the navigation is ready.
        Parameters:
        isRunning - true after NavigationView has been initialized once and began navigation, else false. Indicates that NavigationViewModel is currently running and hasn't been destroyed from a configuration change.
